class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">Anish Kapoor. Copper Sky 2012</figcaption>\n  </figure>\n      </p>\n<p>\n  <figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n  \n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/anish-kapoor-earth-sky-V_zwyes1-9c8345eee24fd9da170ce6f0d2bf6b26-33e24.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; null; max-width: 480px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 137.08333333333334%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px transparent;\"\n        alt=\"anish kapoor earth sky V\"\n        title=\"Anish Kapoor. Earth Sky V 2012\"\n        src=\"/static/anish-kapoor-earth-sky-V_zwyes1-9c8345eee24fd9da170ce6f0d2bf6b26-33e24.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/anish-kapoor-earth-sky-V_zwyes1-9c8345eee24fd9da170ce6f0d2bf6b26-7084e.jpg 200w,\n/static/anish-kapoor-earth-sky-V_zwyes1-9c8345eee24fd9da170ce6f0d2bf6b26-e263b.jpg 400w,\n/static/anish-kapoor-earth-sky-V_zwyes1-9c8345eee24fd9da170ce6f0d2bf6b26-33e24.jpg 480w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 480px) 100vw, 480px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    \n  <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">Anish Kapoor. Earth Sky V 2012</figcaption>\n  </figure>\n      </p>\n<p>\n  <figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n  \n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/anish-kapoor-cement_q3i84l-1b0f93c9437de4a4639099bdd1bd6470-55fd7.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; null; max-width: 640px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 75%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px transparent;\"\n        alt=\"Anish Kapoor. Untitled 2012\"\n        title=\"Anish Kapoor. Untitled 2012\"\n        src=\"/static/anish-kapoor-cement_q3i84l-1b0f93c9437de4a4639099bdd1bd6470-55fd7.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/anish-kapoor-cement_q3i84l-1b0f93c9437de4a4639099bdd1bd6470-e81c0.jpg 200w,\n/static/anish-kapoor-cement_q3i84l-1b0f93c9437de4a4639099bdd1bd6470-8e8ea.jpg 400w,\n/static/anish-kapoor-cement_q3i84l-1b0f93c9437de4a4639099bdd1bd6470-55fd7.jpg 640w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    \n  <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">Anish Kapoor. Untitled 2012</figcaption>\n  </figure>\n      </p>\n<p><strong>2. Floating bowls</strong></p>\n<p>And yet, in another room, there’s a complete turn around with the colourful fiber glass bowls lined up against the walls – here is the same Kapoor we love  – and more so in monochromatic colours, aquamarine, hot orange, lime green!  Has the colourful spot paintings of Damien Hirst finally rubbed on him? No – far from it –  this room spells like a time machine…I observe these bowls from the sides and front – not knowing what to make of these shapes. I feel like I am lost in space. Mars 2012 should be in this room.</p>\n<p>\n  <figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n  \n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/anish-kapoor_two-blues_hollow_fpxqvn-50e79f2e41fe895484cc99f09bb0bf3e-55fd7.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; null; max-width: 640px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 75%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px transparent;\"\n        alt=\"Anish Kapoor: Two Blues 2012 (Left); Hollow 2012 (Right)\"\n        title=\"Anish Kapoor: Two Blues 2012 [Left]; Hollow 2012 [Right]\"\n        src=\"/static/anish-kapoor_two-blues_hollow_fpxqvn-50e79f2e41fe895484cc99f09bb0bf3e-55fd7.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/anish-kapoor_two-blues_hollow_fpxqvn-50e79f2e41fe895484cc99f09bb0bf3e-e81c0.jpg 200w,\n/static/anish-kapoor_two-blues_hollow_fpxqvn-50e79f2e41fe895484cc99f09bb0bf3e-8e8ea.jpg 400w,\n/static/anish-kapoor_two-blues_hollow_fpxqvn-50e79f2e41fe895484cc99f09bb0bf3e-55fd7.jpg 640w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    \n  <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">Anish Kapoor: Two Blues 2012 [Left]; Hollow 2012 [Right]</figcaption>\n  </figure>\n      </p>\n<p>\n  <figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n  \n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/anish-kapoor-_shine_lost_ydswwb-e7f5a81ec0d58dd5ceb72b5dbe3aadd3-55fd7.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; null; max-width: 640px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 75%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px transparent;\"\n        alt=\"Anish Kapoor. Various sculptures\"\n        title=\"Anish Kapoor. Various sculptures\"\n        src=\"/static/anish-kapoor-_shine_lost_ydswwb-e7f5a81ec0d58dd5ceb72b5dbe3aadd3-55fd7.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/anish-kapoor-_shine_lost_ydswwb-e7f5a81ec0d58dd5ceb72b5dbe3aadd3-e81c0.jpg 200w,\n/static/anish-kapoor-_shine_lost_ydswwb-e7f5a81ec0d58dd5ceb72b5dbe3aadd3-8e8ea.jpg 400w,\n/static/anish-kapoor-_shine_lost_ydswwb-e7f5a81ec0d58dd5ceb72b5dbe3aadd3-55fd7.jpg 640w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    \n  <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">Anish Kapoor. Various sculptures</figcaption>\n  </figure>\n      </p>\n<p><strong>3. Intersection 2012</strong></p>\n<p>In the yard of the Lisson gallery sits a large-scale sculpture – colossal like The Orbit and made of the same material, Corten steel. The large opening invites you to come along and take a peek inside but stops you from going inside once you see the small hole in the intersection.</p>\n<p>\n  <figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n  \n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/anish-kapoor_intersection-1_hxwjuj-45ed5252ceaa76caea10e94714e7ce1c-55fd7.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; null; max-width: 640px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 75%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px transparent;\"\n        alt=\"anish kapoor_intersection 1\"\n        title=\"Anish Kapoor intersection\"\n        src=\"/static/anish-kapoor_intersection-1_hxwjuj-45ed5252ceaa76caea10e94714e7ce1c-55fd7.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/anish-kapoor_intersection-1_hxwjuj-45ed5252ceaa76caea10e94714e7ce1c-e81c0.jpg 200w,\n/static/anish-kapoor_intersection-1_hxwjuj-45ed5252ceaa76caea10e94714e7ce1c-8e8ea.jpg 400w,\n/static/anish-kapoor_intersection-1_hxwjuj-45ed5252ceaa76caea10e94714e7ce1c-55fd7.jpg 640w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    \n  <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">Anish Kapoor intersection</figcaption>\n  </figure>\n      </p>\n<p><strong>4. Organ 2012</strong></p>\n<p>The first ever ready-made sculpture from Kapoor – it’s a diesel engine and looks like a misplaced object in this sea of earth-like installations and resin-made sculptures. Crouched in a corner, this machine looks impersonal and devoid of any emotion. It clearly doesn’t belong here and yet it does, which is a point of discourse. Why Anish has suddenly ventured into ready-made sculptures is mind-blogging. Maybe he’s laughing at us now for this intended parody?</p>\n<p>\n  <figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n  \n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/anish-kapoor_organ_yqvuwv-0c5fcaddcde33540d60a4cfc554bf8ff-55fd7.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; null; max-width: 640px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 75%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px transparent;\"\n        alt=\"anish kapoor organ\"\n        title=\"Anish Kapoor organ\"\n        src=\"/static/anish-kapoor_organ_yqvuwv-0c5fcaddcde33540d60a4cfc554bf8ff-55fd7.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/anish-kapoor_organ_yqvuwv-0c5fcaddcde33540d60a4cfc554bf8ff-e81c0.jpg 200w,\n/static/anish-kapoor_organ_yqvuwv-0c5fcaddcde33540d60a4cfc554bf8ff-8e8ea.jpg 400w,\n/static/anish-kapoor_organ_yqvuwv-0c5fcaddcde33540d60a4cfc554bf8ff-55fd7.jpg 640w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    \n  <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">Anish Kapoor organ</figcaption>\n  </figure>\n      </p>\n<p><strong>5. Anxiety</strong></p>\n<p>An installation in a very dark room can already give you some sort of claustrophobia. A bright light is projected unto the floor which strangely highlights its organic and earth-like surface.</p>\n<p>\n  <figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n  \n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/anish-kapoor_anxious_ftvrwh-1707a8698dd340c300d8da2ff8ba5135-33e24.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; null; max-width: 480px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 133.33333333333331%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px transparent;\"\n        alt=\"anish kapoor anxious\"\n        title=\"Anish Kapoor anxious\"\n        src=\"/static/anish-kapoor_anxious_ftvrwh-1707a8698dd340c300d8da2ff8ba5135-33e24.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/anish-kapoor_anxious_ftvrwh-1707a8698dd340c300d8da2ff8ba5135-7084e.jpg 200w,\n/static/anish-kapoor_anxious_ftvrwh-1707a8698dd340c300d8da2ff8ba5135-e263b.jpg 400w,\n/static/anish-kapoor_anxious_ftvrwh-1707a8698dd340c300d8da2ff8ba5135-33e24.jpg 480w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 480px) 100vw, 480px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    \n  <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">Anish Kapoor anxious</figcaption>\n  </figure>\n      </p>\n<p>Read more:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/art/reviews/anish-kapoor-lisson-gallery-london-8204042.html\">Independent: Anish Kapoor Lisson Gallery</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://omg.yahoo.com/photos/artist-anish-kapoor-poses-next-piece-intersection-2012-photo-140237182.html\">Omg yahoo: Anish Kapoor Intersection 2012 (Photo)</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://londonist.com/2012/10/art-review-anish-kapoor-lisson-gallery.php\">Londonist: Art review Anish Kapoor</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://arrestedmotion.com/2012/10/showing-anish-kapoor-lisson-gallery/\">Arrested Motion: Anish Kapoor (Lisson gallery)</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.designboom.com/weblog/cat/10/view/24183/anish-kapoor-at-lisson-gallery.html\">Design Boom: Anish Kapoor</a></li>\n</ul>","fields":{"slug":"/